OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776258665
OL,3,CLast-minute bookings surge as
OL,4,Cholidaymakers choose to stay in the UK
OL,6,FKate Walby reports from across Cumbria.
OL,8,FHoliday bookings in Cumbria over the
OL,9,FEaster holidays suggest that locals
OL,10,Fand tourists chose to holiday in their
OL,11,Fown country, amid rising costs and
OL,12,Fglobal uncertainty.
OL,14,FIn one Bassenthwaite holiday park, all
OL,15,F56 lodges were full over the Easter
OL,16,Fbreak, but a third of domestic
OL,17,Fbookings were made only one day before
OL,18,Ftravel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
