OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776258665
OL,3,CLast-minute bookings surge as
OL,4,Cholidaymakers choose to stay in the UK
OL,6,FThis experience is seen nationally,
OL,7,Fwith figures from holiday rentals
OL,8,Fgroup Awaze show domestic bookings
OL,9,Fmade the day before departure
OL,10,Fincreased by 33% year-on-year in the
OL,11,Ftwo weeks leading up to Easter for
OL,12,FMarch arrivals.
OL,14,FThese figures also show that more than
OL,15,Fa fifth - 22% - of all UK bookings are
OL,16,Fmade within two weeks of departure.
OL,18,FOne hotel owner believes increases in
OL,19,Fthe cost of living have led tourists
OL,20,Fto escape the traditional hotspots and
OL,21,Fexplore less popular areas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
