PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776258665
OL,3,CLast-minute bookings surge as
OL,4,Cholidaymakers choose to stay in the UK
OL,6,FAdrian Rome, the manager of a St Bees
OL,7,Fhotel, told ITV Border: "There's a
OL,8,Fgreater demand for tourism on the west
OL,9,Fcoast of Cumbria than there ever has
OL,10,Fbeen.
OL,12,F"The central lakes have become more
OL,13,Fexpensive, and I think it's become a
OL,14,Flittle bit of a discovery of the gem
OL,15,Fof the western coast - it's become
OL,16,Fmore and more attractive."
OL,18,FThe Managing Director of Cumbria
OL,19,FTourism says it is too early to make
OL,20,Fany predictions for the summer
OL,21,Fholidays, however.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
