FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776258665
OL,3,CLast-minute bookings surge as
OL,4,Cholidaymakers choose to stay in the UK
OL,6,FGill Haigh told ITV Border: "What we
OL,7,Fsaw just before Easter is that quite a
OL,8,Fnumber of people chose to postpone
OL,9,Ftheir international holidays.
OL,11,F"Whether people will choose to travel
OL,12,Fabroad later in the year, we'll have
OL,13,Fsee how that plays out."
OL,15,FGemma Brown from Awaze said: "Post
OL,16,FCovid there was a spike across the UK
OL,17,Fin bookings, but it's been resilient
OL,18,Fever since.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
