PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1776258665
OL,3,CLast-minute bookings surge as
OL,4,Cholidaymakers choose to stay in the UK
OL,6,F"A lot of owners have really
OL,7,Fdiversified the product - it's high
OL,8,Fquality accommodation you can immerse
OL,9,Fyourself in.
OL,11,F"I think a lot of people are seeking
OL,12,Fspace where you can gather friends and
OL,13,Ffamily together, and the UK provides
OL,14,Fthat place where you can bring your
OL,15,Fdog with you.
OL,17,F"The last thing people want to
OL,18,Fsacrifice is a holiday."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
